overview: In the modern utopia of Objectia, two siblings, a narcissistic Spade, and a cynical Bucket are just barely getting by in the harsh city. One works tirelessly, while the other sits on his butt eating nachos. After a heated argument, Bucket kicks out the reluctant Spade in order to force him to work. With the help of his best friend Map, Spade must set out in the inanimate world to find himself a place to work. It's then when they meet a strange individual do things get... Troublesome.
title: Diggin' Up Trouble
